KIBO PERSONALIZATION

Kibo Personalization, powered byMonetateandCertona, is the leading personalization software, recognized by key industry analysts.

From sophisticated A/B testing to AI-driven personalization, harness patented technology to delight your customers with impactful individualized experiences, resulting in increased engagement, conversions, and lifetime value.

JOIN TODAY

SHAPE CUSTOMER EXPERIENCES THAT DELIVER

Build More Valuable Audiences

Create audience segments based on behavior, context, 1st- and 3rd-party data, and more. Work alongside AI to discover and build deeper, more valuable audiences for more expansive personalization opportunities.

Experiment And Optimize Without Limits

Go beyond A/B testing with machine learningavoid having to wait for statistical significance, reduce risk and adapt to fluctuating consumer behaviors by auto-allocating your traffic to winning variants.

Delight Shoppers With Individualized CX

Lean on the power of machine learning to optimize content, messaging and layouts to individual users. Deliver powerful experiences and uncover new insights within user-friendly builders and dashboards.

MONETATE IS NOW KIBO!

As you know, Monetate is now Kibo Personalization and integrated into our Unified Commerce Platform. With Kibo you can deliver omnichannel experiences with Kibo Personalization, powered by Monetate and Certona, that are personalized across the full customer journey.

We’ve brought in market-leading features from Certona alongside exciting feature releases like Social Proof and Core SDKs, and there’s much more to come! Combining best-in-class recommendations, robust testing, in-depth targeting, and ML-powered personalization into one unified platform equips you to more easily deliver cross-channel experiences that deliver results.
